[Enable Debug Menus [Read Note]]
author=punk7890
description=This code replaces the pause menu in game. Press one of the following to enable a menu:

*L3 + D-Pad Up for Debug Cheat Menu.
*L3 + D-Pad Right for Debug Room Menu.
*L3 + D-Pad Left for Debug Spawn Menu.
*L3 + D-Pad Down for normal pause menu.
